tasks.description:
Create .mcp.json in the project root for Claude Code to auto-discover the Cassini MCP server.

Contents:
```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "cassini": {
      "type": "stdio",
      "command": "bun",
      "args": ["run", "mcp/src/index.ts"],
      "env": {
        "DATABASE_PATH": "./cassini.db"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Also save the implementation plan to docs/plans/cassini-mcp.md for reference. The plan should document: the database schema, the 3 tools exposed, design decisions (read-only, no compile step, row limit, separate package, bun:sqlite), and how to configure for Claude Desktop.
